DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bxwwl.com,REJECT-TINYGIF
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cecsc1.com,REJECT-TINYGIF
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,sdchb2.com,REJECT-TINYGIF
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,renzhen8.cn,REJECT-TINYGIF
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,m4pgay.com,REJECT-TINYGIF
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,qbhmz3.com,REJECT-TINYGIF
